{"tid":1533402,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「討論」中共無牌可以出，切勿接受階段性勝利","createTime":"2019-09-02T17:11:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T17:31:38.000Z","uid":75461,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7bfe042597a01e2637be5bc2bd69a9a9f54b1c94","tid":1533402,"uid":75461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:11:13.000Z","msg":"唔知有無人post過，tg見到呢個：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/iamchinese2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fiamchinese2&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgYhgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=09f27fef\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/iamchinese2</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vyTqdcX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvyTqdcX.png&h=3c1f2f01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加埋路透社留出7婆錄音，睇得出中共唔會出老解，架空7婆同只能靠黑警繼續打壓。各位手足一定要keep住推香港議題上國際打長期戰。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">重點：停止抗爭做中共順民只會輸一世。中共係唔會比香港人有高度自治權。再次提醒大家不要接受階段性勝利</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n即使平息咗呢次戰爭，香港再唔係以前的香港啦，即使清算到黑警，可為義士平反，但唔係雙普選的話<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">歷史只會重演！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n香港人加油，萬事小心。</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"cc262742138447ed4ddf0bfbf15ab3e33bde6be3","tid":1533402,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:11:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/katsugatsuk/status/1168566212420259840\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkatsugatsuk%2Fstatus%2F1168566212420259840&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgYhgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=bdcd7ce6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkatsugatsuk%2Fstatus%2F1168566212420259840&h=1db366b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/katsugatsuk/status/1168566212420259840</a><br />\n日文版 都出埋<br />\n班垃圾食狗糧食到跳18銅人舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" c